-- Boston Mayor Menino Cancels School Tomorrow Before Snow Storm
-- B y   A n n i e   L i n s k e y
-- 2013-02-07T17:53:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-07/boston-mayor-menino-cancels-school-tomorrow-before-snow-storm.html
Boston Mayor Thomas Menino canceled
school tomorrow and urged residents to take public transit
rather than drive before a “historic” snow storm threatening
the region.
* Menino says 900 pieces of equipment will be on streets by 9pm
tomorrow to clear snow
* Menino declares snow emergency from noon tomorrow
* Boston expecting as much as 2 feet of snow, according to the
National Weather Service.
* New York City may get almost a foot  To contact the reporter on this story:
